Cinnamon Sandhu, an artist of South Asian-Canadian descent, possesses a unique blend of talents as a singer, songwriter, and composer. Her discography spans various genres, embracing Punjabi pop, R&B, English pop, and soulful acoustic sounds from different corners of the globe. ⁠
⁠
Cinnamon's musical journey began in her childhood when she was placed in Indian music singing lessons. She developed a passion for writing songs and honed her skills by recording covers. Motivated by the substantial support she garnered from social media platforms; Cinnamon Sandhu decided to independently release her own original music. Her debut EP, titled "Love Story," has recently become available in all major music stores, marking an important milestone in Cinnamon's journey as a promising and emerging artist.
